text: Markt Indersdorf station is a railway station in the Karpfhofen district in the municipality of Markt Indersdorf, located in the district of Dachau in Upper Bavaria, Germany. ==References== ==External links== Category:Munich S-Bahn stations Category:Railway stations in Bavaria Category:Railway stations in Germany opened in 1912 Category:Buildings and structures in Dachau (district)
